        "Cigarette is not only harmful to the people who consume them, but also to those  around the consumers  who smoke should be banned in public facilities. I totally agree with this statement because of some aspects.",
        "To begin with, smoking has many worse effects ,especially on people's bodies. A cigarette is able to cause many diseases such as respiratory disease and throat disease. These diseases are really detrimental and can cause  decreasing productivity of people when they affect disease because of cigarettes. To take an example, there are a lot of people who suffered from consuming  cigarettes, and all of them regret why they consumed cigarettes in the past. As a result, their productivity decrease to this trend and they feel hopeless because of the disease.",
