        "To sum up, we know that smoking is not only dangerous for  smokers, but also for their surroundings. Suffering because of disease is one example of smoking, and cigarettes are supposed to be banned from public facilities such as schools, bus stations, and airports by making strict rules for the smoker in order that the number of people who suffer from this trend can be decreased slightly. I believe that when this solution is made, it will make the number of consumers of cigarettes decrease."
